17 Hours Ago “The blood of Miss Heritage Ajibola is on the management of the Hostel and we hold them accountable for the events. “The situation should be seen as an urge to muster the hostel management of the school to improve in their affairs with managing the school hostel as the health of the students should be a priority to the school management. Bver hostel, a private hostel erected on the university’s property. “The NANS Southwest believes that the university management under the leadership of the Vice Chancellor, Prof. Eyitope Ogunbodede should have done a good job checking the structural standard of the hostels before accommodating the Nigerian students. A welfare committee on off campus hostel should have been effected by the management. “We are using this medium to sympathise with the family of the late student and also urge the school to see to avoiding such incident later in future. We demand justice for our sister and friend whom the management of the Hostel has sent on an untimely errand.”